RC Double proppeler helicopter project controlled by a Playstation 2 controller over a XBee transmission

You will need the PSX_lib developped by Bill Porter (http://www.billporter.info/)

Needed : 
	* Arduino Nano for the controller
	* Arduino Mega for the helicopter core
	* Playstation 2 controller

Commit 05/29/12:
 	+ Throttle command frame (PWN)
        + Modification of the PWN ports
